Belgium wunderkind Eptic joins the big boys and releases his debut EP for Never Say Die. These four dubplates of fire will ignite any dancefloor or schoolyard. As has been proved by the lucky sods who have had them for the past few months -(Dillon Francis, Flux Pavilion, Cookie Monsta and SKisM are just a handful of such sods.) Including the Internet sensation 'Like a Boss', this is the coming of age release for the 18 year old... wait...18 f*cking years old!? Yes, while most of us were furiously chasing girls and eating sweets at this tender age, Michael Bella is setting himself up for Dubstep super stardom.
